    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089740/extras/42ebb249090261408e65090f3cadc53e.webp?t=1767392867\" width=600 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use a lighter and a fuel canister to light your way and burn everything and everyone that stands between you and your goal, because sometimes the only way to survive is to leave behind only ashes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089740/extras/5f850d90bd89fad66b58fcd490e64749.webp?t=1767392867\" width=600 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every word or sound you make can give you away. Enemies can hear you. Keep this in mind when choosing your tactics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The toolkit of sound devices that you can buy in the game store can be very useful in the fight against all enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089740/extras/c6baaa23e903f4612784bd2ea0c68050.webp?t=1767392867\" width=600 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each player starts the game alone, you don't know where you are, you don't know who you will meet on your way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In each game session, the city changes its landscape, which guarantees the uniqueness of each passage and makes you rely solely on your intuition when any next turning point could be the last.</p>",
